{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["Linux"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DocumentConfiguration"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To instruct OpenAPIKit to decode OpenAPI Standards versions it does not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"natively support, set ","type":"text"},{"code":"userInfo[DocumentConfiguration.versionMapKey] = [\"3.5.0\": OpenAPI.Document.Version.v3_1_1]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"That will cause OpenAPIKit to accept OAS v3.5.0 on decode and treat it as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the natively supported v3.1.1. This feature exists to allow OpenAPIKit to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be configured to parse future versions of the OAS standard that are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"determined (by you) to be backwards compatible with a previous version","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"prior to OpenAPIKit gaining official support for the new version and its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"features.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/DocumentConfiguration"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openapikit\/documentconfiguration"]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/DocumentConfiguration\/versionMapKey"],"title":"Type Properties"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DocumentConfiguration"}],"modules